# Sales Performance Dashboard - Excel Project
![Sales Performance Dashboard](/nandita-sharma-portfolio/asset/Excel_Sales_Dashboard.png) 

### Description

The Sales Performance Dashboard is an Excel-based solution designed to analyze and visualize sales performance metrics for informed decision-making. Leveraging the combined power of Excel, Power Pivot, Excel functions, and VLOOKUP, this dashboard provides actionable insights into sales trends, product performance, customer segmentation, and more. It offers a user-friendly interface for interactive exploration and deep dive analysis, empowering stakeholders to drive business growth and optimize sales strategies.

### Key Features

- **Dynamic Dashboard**: Explore sales performance metrics dynamically through interactive charts, graphs, and tables.
- **Data Modeling with Power Pivot**: Utilize Power Pivot for advanced data modeling and aggregation to handle large datasets efficiently.
- **Excel Functions and Formulas**: Leverage Excel functions and formulas to calculate key performance indicators (KPIs) and derive meaningful insights.
- **VLOOKUP for Data Integration**: Utilize VLOOKUP to integrate data from multiple sources and enhance data analysis capabilities.
- **Customizable Reporting**: Customize the dashboard layout, visuals, and calculations to meet specific business requirements and analysis needs.
- **Automatic Data Refresh**: Set up automatic data refresh to keep the dashboard updated with the latest sales data.
